{"tid":609392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[動保撚請進］毛孩守護者捕獸籠困狗 村民報警","createTime":"2018-03-29T04:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T13:40:38.000Z","uid":6497,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac1aa2fe82e010c5b535ff6ed0f16d112ad1112","tid":609392,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180329/large/1522294899_ba9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180329%2Flarge%2F1522294899_ba9e.jpg&h=9bf6c950&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180329/large/1522294901_2563.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180329%2Flarge%2F1522294901_2563.jpg&h=52e9f013&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180329/large/1522294902_14a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180329%2Flarge%2F1522294902_14a8.jpg&h=d25aa10b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早上11時16分，大嶼山白芒一名村民致電愛護動物協會，指在一條通往東涌的行山徑上，發現一個捕獸籠，裡面有一隻唐狗，擔心牠沒有水飲。愛協職員到場，見捕獸籠內有一兜飯，籠有鐵鏈上鎖，無法將狗放出來，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n捕獸籠上有告示，指鐵籠屬於毛孩守護者，留有聯絡電話。兩名毛孩守護者的職員到場，包括組織創辦人兼董事陸家捷，他們也承認捕獸籠是他們擺放，用意是引一隻目標母狗入籠，以便替牠進行絕育手術。不過，法例規定任何人不得放置捕獸器，警方正在場調查，暫列虐畜。<br />\n<br />\n法例規定，任何人未獲漁護署授權，或未向該署申領狩獵牌照，擅自裝置或使用捕獸器，不論放置在郊野公園或其他地方用作捕捉受保護動物，均屬違法。非法藏有捕獸器，一經定罪最高可被罰款5萬元；若捕獲受保護動物，更可被罰款10萬元及監禁1年。"},{"pid":"48a54cc7f50a25b8c2340b2d7529bc465b29fc63","tid":609392,"uid":47268,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:24:52.000Z","msg":"毛孩撚真係好撚仆街"},{"pid":"acd33463c5220b2559385de9848b9b67c381921b","tid":609392,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48a54cc7f50a25b8c2340b2d7529bc465b29fc63","tid":609392,"uid":47268,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:24:52.000Z","msg":"毛孩撚真係好撚仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:49:25.000Z","msg":"虐畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3751a1f516d338f059664aa85bfd1af20f7342a5","tid":609392,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acd33463c5220b2559385de9848b9b67c381921b","tid":609392,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48a54cc7f50a25b8c2340b2d7529bc465b29fc63","tid":609392,"uid":47268,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:24:52.000Z","msg":"毛孩撚真係好撚仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:49:25.000Z","msg":"虐畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5e5c6e005e7a6f1cf050089eb52e08fa48e9a5","tid":609392,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"絕育撚死全家"},{"pid":"b12fb554ab475216517a7550a1775d7a2a4cec92","tid":609392,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"又食狗血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22da55d75ec9efb7c6eec657f2a5ebf4f26cab69","tid":609392,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:40:38.000Z","msg":"毛孩唔係幫狼人症病人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}